story_alola_01_11000/2401_1001_0200_10: Now’s not the time to space out, Mina!
story_alola_01_11000/2401_1001_0300_10: Tapu Fini wants to lend you its strength!
story_alola_01_11000/2401_1001_0800_10: We’d better retreat if we’re up against a tapu!
story_alola_01_11000/2401_1001_1100_10: Thank you, Tapu Fini. You saved me again.
story_alola_01_11000/2401_1001_1300_10:
You know how people living on Poni Island are
pretty much protected by Tapu Fini?
story_alola_01_11000/2401_1001_1400_10:
Hapu, have you ever heard that story about the
kid who almost drowned on Poni...
story_alola_01_11000/2401_1001_1500_10: and was saved by Tapu Fini?
story_alola_01_11000/2401_1001_1600_10: Do you mean that child was...
story_alola_01_11000/2401_1001_1700_10: Ah. I won’t press any further.
story_alola_01_11000/2401_1001_1800_10:
This Tapu Fini does appear to be different from the
guardian deity in Alola.
story_alola_01_11000/2401_1001_2000_10:
And yet, no matter what, as someone who
resides in Alola, our desire to respect Pokémon
remains unwavering.
story_alola_01_11000/2401_1001_2200_10:
The assistance was not just one-sided. You
two battled together.
story_alola_01_11000/2401_1001_2300_10: It wasn’t “again”—you have taken a step forward.
story_alola_01_11000/2401_1001_2500_10: And, Tapu Fini, I gotta say...
story_alola_01_11000/2401_1001_2600_10:
Whatever beach you’re on, you’d make a
pretty great painting!
